{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "16.0",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9a5ff31c",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "さあ、ズボンとパンツを脱ぎなさいっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "edb88c96",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突然部屋のドアが勢いよく開くと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.2",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "edb88c96",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "唐突にヘンな要求をしてくるフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.4",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "edb88c96",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その両手にはピンク色の何かを握っていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "21.0",
      "line_index": 21,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "42a3a84",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──はぁっ！？　突然現れてなんてこと言うんだよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b4e7fe52",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "いいから黙って脱いでっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "b04328c3",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ちょ……！！　ズボン引っ張らないでくれぇっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.0",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d5ab369",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "だったら脱いでよっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.0",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e1fcae",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "わ、わかったから……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "37.2",
      "line_index": 37,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9e1fcae",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でもその前に理由くらい教えてくれ、唐突過ぎるんだよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "977f514c",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "搾精のためよ、あなたの精液が欲しいの",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3c7b2d59",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "はぁ……！？　せっ精液ぃ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.0",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a7ecbb99",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そうよ、魔科学の研究に必要なの。男性の精液って触媒として有能なのよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "53.0",
      "line_index": 53,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f078010f",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "それでこのオナホールでシコシコして……精液を貰いたいってわけ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.0",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87f27a6b",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そういうわけだから……はい、ズボン脱いで",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "59.0",
      "line_index": 59,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2fde01e2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ま、待って！　搾精って言われても……！　それって……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fc2dc8e6",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "へ、ヘンな勘違いはしないでよね！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.2",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "fc2dc8e6",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "私はただ純粋に精液が欲しいだけなのっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7c84fc73",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "それに一応誰彼構わず欲しがってなんていないから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "190e6eb4",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "あなただから頼んでるだけ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.2",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "190e6eb4",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そ、それだけなのよっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3de3a05",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーは頬を紅く染め、上目使いに見つめてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.2",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3de3a05",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そこにはいつもの高飛車なフォニーではなく、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.4",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "3de3a05",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おねだりをする可愛らしい女の子がいた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ee4e274",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その姿に心臓の鼓動が早くなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.2",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ee4e274",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーにオナホでされるのを想像するだけで",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.4",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "ee4e274",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "股間が反応してしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "78.0",
      "line_index": 78,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "17e8a760",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ねぇ……お願い……あなたの精液ちょうだい",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "81.0",
      "line_index": 81,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8fc8f3ce",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そ、それは……その……そのくらいなら別に……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a1ae2a2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーのおねだりと性欲に負け思わず頷いてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "88.0",
      "line_index": 88,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "39cdcb30",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ほ、ほんと！？　やった！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "91.0",
      "line_index": 91,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9e8875ce",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でも、その……されるってのは……一人でやるんじゃダメなのか……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "96.0",
      "line_index": 96,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8426a30b",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "良質な精液を得るには性感の高まり方も重要なの",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "99.0",
      "line_index": 99,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1c2142f2",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "あなたのオナニーでは任せられないわっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.0",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bae6a6c7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "おねだりをしながらも冷静な風を装ってはいるフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "101.2",
      "line_index": 101,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "bae6a6c7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし額には大粒の汗が浮かべ、僅かに身体を震わせていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "104.0",
      "line_index": 104,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9c3cfe1a",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（フォニー緊張してるんだ……普段はそんな様子見せないのに……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "73f5a8c7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなフォニーにさらにドキドキが強くなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.2",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "73f5a8c7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして気がつけばベルトをガチャガチャと外してしまっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "111.0",
      "line_index": 111,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d6fe8b73",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "い、いいの……？　精液くれるの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.0",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6bf50902",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……結構恥ずかしいけど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "114.2",
      "line_index": 114,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6bf50902",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "でもフォニーがそこまで求めるなら……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a9832ba7",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "だ、だったら最初から素直にズボン脱ぎなさいよっ、このノロマ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d36657e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "照れ隠しにプイっと顔を背け怒るフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.2",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "9d36657e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そんなフォニーの態度にさらに興奮を覚え、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.4",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "9d36657e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ズボンとパンツを脱ぎ捨てると、肥大化した股間を露にした。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "37ab9986",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ん……んん……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.0",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f29465e3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒が柔らかなものに包まれ、腰がビクンと跳ねる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "138.2",
      "line_index": 138,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f29465e3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "締め付けるような圧迫感が、何とも言えない快感をもたらしてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "141.0",
      "line_index": 141,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2445a6c1",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "入った……サイズは少し小さ目かもだけど問題無いわよね？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "484564f7",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "た、たぶん……オナホ初めてで勝手がよくわからないけど……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "148.0",
      "line_index": 148,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "87098c2a",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "わ、私だって初めてよ……！　こんなこと今まで誰にも……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ffee8bb",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ……フォニー……その、胸……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "650bcd0a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーの小さな胸が視界に飛び込み、肉棒がビクンと跳ねる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.2",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "650bcd0a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白な乳房に、ピンク色の小さな突起物、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.4",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "650bcd0a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それを見ているだけで胸の鼓動がどこまでも早く強くなる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "342631e8",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "こっこれは……！　こ、こっちの方があんたが興奮できるでしょ！？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "160.0",
      "line_index": 160,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2d10e5b4",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "良質な精液には男性の興奮が一番重要なのっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.0",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3fc77400",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "本当は見せたくないけど、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "163.2",
      "line_index": 163,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "3fc77400",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "こ、これも研究のためなんだから、勘違いしないでよねっ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "166.0",
      "line_index": 166,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "be619fec",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "──ううっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.0",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "84d04a37",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "オナホをぎゅっと握りしめられ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "169.2",
      "line_index": 169,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "84d04a37",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "思わず口から声が漏れてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bac182a0",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "あっ！？　そ、その、い、痛かった……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "175.0",
      "line_index": 175,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "79ac5e11",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "いや……そういうわけじゃ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1fa64bb2",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "そ、そう、なの……それなら何も問題はないわね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.0",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "24cac79",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "それにしてもなんて大きいの……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.2",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "24cac79",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "想像の何倍も大きくて、硬い……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2ceb95e",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "でもこのままじゃ射精しないわよね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.2",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2ceb95e",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "それじゃあ始めるわよ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "193.0",
      "line_index": 193,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "76f7d956",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う……くぅ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.0",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d2bf3ff1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーはゆっくりとオナホを動かすと、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "196.2",
      "line_index": 196,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d2bf3ff1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゾクっとした刺激が全身を駆ける。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34cada41",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "肉棒がフォニーの小さな手の中でビクンと何度も跳ねあがり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.2",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "34cada41",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そのたびに心配そうにこちらを見つめてくる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.0",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec04181e",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "ふ、ふふん♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "201.2",
      "line_index": 201,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ec04181e",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "結構その……感じているよね？♥　おちんちん跳ねてるし",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "204.0",
      "line_index": 204,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "aabe43f8",
      "speaker": "フォニー",
      "ja": "男性を射精させるのって案外たいしたことないのかも……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.0",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "47a7e861",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少しずつオナホを動かす速度を上げていくフォニー。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.2",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "47a7e861",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "フォニーの小さな手で肉棒を扱かれる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "206.4",
      "line_index": 206,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "47a7e861",
      "speaker": "",
